    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46688</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_196_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いちち……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Owie...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_196_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大丈夫、&lt;Dio&gt;？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Are you alright, &lt;Dio&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46864</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_196_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>全然だいじょーぶだって！
んなの、ツバつけときゃ治るって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Everything's fine! Nothing a little licking can't fix.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46980</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_196_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダメだよ！　ばい菌入ったらどうすんの？
ちゃんと処置しないと！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You can't! What if germs get in! That's going
to cause an infection! We gotta treat it properly.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47120</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_196_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んだんだ、おめぇが怪我するのは勝手だが、
&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;に余計な心配掛けんじゃねぇよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Great, now you've gone ahead and wounded yourself,
can you not make &lt;Mel&gt; worry even more?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47188</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_196_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ったく……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Tch...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47252</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_196_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ほら、見せて</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Okay, show it to me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47332</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_196_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……おい、今のってまさか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey...wasn't that just a...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47488</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_196_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんぐれぇのキズ、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;に頼るなんて贅沢だ。
おらの屁ぇ掛けときゃ治るだーよ。ぶひゃひゃひゃ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Be grateful! &lt;Mel&gt;'s kiss is one of the greatest luxuries
you can rely on. If it were me, just a fart would be enough!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47604</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_196_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>てめぇ、ふざけんじゃねぇ！
とっ捕まえて、ぶっ飛ばしてやる！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>D-Don't you dare even th-think about it!
Try something like that and I'll send you flying!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47680</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_196_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あのふたりは……もう……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Those two are...really...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_196_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……困ったもんだね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A pain...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
